This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on the task of Complex Word Identification (CWI). Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society) as these fields are also relevant to the study of NLP and the development of algorithms for text simplification.
